RawLine: SDM_1101924013,首先深吸一口氣，調勻內息。接著氣走太虛穴，衝擊穴位，再循著經絡，將氣運至手三里穴。,首先深吸一口气，调匀内息。接着气走太虚穴，冲击穴位，再循着经络，将气运至手三里穴。

Items.mt: First, take a deep breath and even out your internal breath. Then you walk through the Taixu point, hit the acupuncture point, and then follow the meridians to carry the Qi to the Hand Three Mile point.
